member.summary:
Handles JsonP requests when requests are fired with text/javascript and 
the query string contains a 'callback' parameter.
Necessary for cross-domain javascript execution.
Add it to your project in the Application_Start section of Global.asax with:
// add jsonp formatter support. needs to go ahead of other json formatters!
GlobalConfiguration.Configuration.Formatters.Insert(0, new BIACore.Web.MediaFormatter.JsonpFormatter());
